      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOLAN (1) resumes today after filling a minor placing at his only appearance last prep at Townsville over 1000m on January 6. Top strike rate at the journey with two wins and four placings from six starts and is sure to go well. BETTER NOT FORGET (7) resumes from a spell of 11 weeks and is having his first outing under new trainer Kris Thomas. Finished fifth at Beaudesert over 1200m at the opening run last time in work. Among the better hopes while fresh. OFFICE POLITICS (3) is ready to win after he just missed last time, beaten a long neck into second over 1000m at Emerald. Nicely placed to feature in the finish. PRO FORMA (4) has been out of the placings in two runs since a break, the latest when tenth, beaten 4.5 lengths, over 1200m at Townsville after he was in the firing line on the turn. Should be peaking now and can find winning form this time.",
